{
  "packId": "english:quote-drills:core",
  "languageId": "english",
  "contentFamilyId": "quote-drills",
  "tier": "core",
  "version": "2026-03-17-public-corpus-v3",
  "entryCount": 96,
  "entries": [
    {
      "text": "The last tie was broken.",
      "signature": ".abehiklnorstw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "foundational"
    },
    {
      "text": "They never did it again.",
      "signature": ".adeghinrtvy",
      "openingToken": "they",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "foundational"
    },
    {
      "text": "They threw clubs at him.",
      "signature": ".abcehilmrstuwy",
      "openingToken": "they",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "foundational"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" Alice ventured to ask.",
      "signature": ".\"acdeiklnorstuv",
      "openingToken": "alice",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" Alice went on eagerly.",
      "signature": ".\"acegilnortwy",
      "openingToken": "alice",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" cried the Mock Turtle.",
      "signature": ".\"cdehiklmortu",
      "openingToken": "cried",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said Alice to herself.",
      "signature": ".\"acdefhilorst",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said the King sharply.",
      "signature": ".\"adeghiklnprsty",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said the Lory hastily.",
      "signature": ".\"adehilorsty",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"What a curious feeling!",
      "signature": "!\"acefghilnorstuw",
      "openingToken": "what",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hyde, a little hoarsely.",
      "signature": ",.adehilorsty",
      "openingToken": "hyde",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Thornton alone held him.",
      "signature": ".adehilmnort",
      "openingToken": "thornton",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Thornton shook his head.",
      "signature": ".adehiknorst",
      "openingToken": "thornton",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Then the Dormouse shall!",
      "signature": "!\"adehlmnorstu",
      "openingToken": "then",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "A revolver-shot rang out.",
      "signature": "-.aeghlnorstuv",
      "openingToken": "a",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Never heard of uglifying!",
      "signature": "!adefghilnoruvy",
      "openingToken": "never",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "No accounting for tastes!",
      "signature": "!acefginorstu",
      "openingToken": "no",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The driver was perplexed.",
      "signature": ".adehilprstvwx",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "the Duchess, the Duchess!",
      "signature": ",!cdehstu",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "There's no pleasing them!",
      "signature": "!'aeghilmnoprst",
      "openingToken": "there's",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said the Rabbit angrily.",
      "signature": ".\"abdeghilnrsty",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "can hardly be exaggerated.",
      "signature": ".abcdeghlnrtxy",
      "openingToken": "can",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Everybody looked at Alice.",
      "signature": ".abcdeiklortvy",
      "openingToken": "everybody",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Next came official orders.",
      "signature": ".acdefilmnorstx",
      "openingToken": "next",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Pike made painful efforts.",
      "signature": ".adefiklmnoprstu",
      "openingToken": "pike",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Presently she began again.",
      "signature": ".abeghilnprsty",
      "openingToken": "presently",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spitz was equally willing.",
      "signature": ".aegilnpqstuwyz",
      "openingToken": "spitz",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" Alice thought to herself.",
      "signature": ".\"acefghilorstu",
      "openingToken": "alice",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" But she waited patiently.",
      "signature": ".\"abdehilnpstuwy",
      "openingToken": "but",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" his scaly friend replied.",
      "signature": ".\"acdefhilnprsy",
      "openingToken": "his",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" thought Alice to herself.",
      "signature": ".\"acefghilorstu",
      "openingToken": "thought",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said the lawyer peevishly.",
      "signature": ".\"adehilprstvwy",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" the Mock Turtle persisted.",
      "signature": ".\"cdehiklmoprstu",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 4,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" And then he begged Mr.",
      "signature": ".\"abdeghmnrt",
      "openingToken": "and",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" but they gave no heed.",
      "signature": ".\"abdeghnotuvy",
      "openingToken": "but",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" one of the jury asked.",
      "signature": ".\"adefhjknorstuy",
      "openingToken": "one",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"And now which is which?",
      "signature": "?\"acdhinosw",
      "openingToken": "and",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"He meant to murder you.",
      "signature": ".\"adehmnortuy",
      "openingToken": "he",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"How are you getting on?",
      "signature": "?\"aeghinortuwy",
      "openingToken": "how",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"I trust you are better.",
      "signature": ".\"abeiorstuy",
      "openingToken": "i",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Who are you talking to?",
      "signature": "?\"aeghiklnortuwy",
      "openingToken": "who",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Also, the dogs were fed.",
      "signature": ",.adefghlorstw",
      "openingToken": "also",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "At night, camp was made.",
      "signature": ",.acdeghimnpstw",
      "openingToken": "at",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "But it bore no postmark.",
      "signature": ".abeikmnoprstu",
      "openingToken": "but",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "No, there were no tears.",
      "signature": ",.aehnorstw",
      "openingToken": "no",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Shocking murder of an M.",
      "signature": ".acdefghikmnorsu",
      "openingToken": "shocking",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The beast in him roared.",
      "signature": ".abdehimnorst",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The Mock Turtle went on.",
      "signature": ".cehklmnortuw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The sled was broken out.",
      "signature": ".abdehklnorstuw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The whole realm was his.",
      "signature": ".aehilmorstw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "They had died so easily.",
      "signature": ".adehilosty",
      "openingToken": "they",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" about once in a minute.",
      "signature": ".\"abceimnotu",
      "openingToken": "about",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" the King said to Alice.",
      "signature": ".\"acdeghiklnost",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"A cheap sort of present!",
      "signature": "!\"acefhnoprst",
      "openingToken": "a",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Once I heard it weeping!",
      "signature": "!\"acdeghinoprtw",
      "openingToken": "once",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"The Queen will hear you!",
      "signature": "!\"aehilnoqrtuwy",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "And they were proud, too.",
      "signature": ",.adehnoprtuwy",
      "openingToken": "and",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Be seated, if you please.",
      "signature": ",.abdefilopstuy",
      "openingToken": "be",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hyde, blowing in the key.",
      "signature": ",.bdeghiklnotwy",
      "openingToken": "hyde",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "There was a dead silence.",
      "signature": ".acdehilnrstw",
      "openingToken": "there",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" said one of the jurymen.",
      "signature": ".\"adefhijmnorstuy",
      "openingToken": "said",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Does the boots and shoes!",
      "signature": "!\"abdehnost",
      "openingToken": "does",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"That was a narrow escape!",
      "signature": "!\"acehnoprstw",
      "openingToken": "that",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"What are you thinking of?",
      "signature": "?\"aefghiknortuwy",
      "openingToken": "what",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Here the train was halted.",
      "signature": ".adehilnrstw",
      "openingToken": "here",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Nay, the tale grows worse.",
      "signature": ",.aeghlnorstwy",
      "openingToken": "nay",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spitz was wild with wrath.",
      "signature": ".adhilprstwz",
      "openingToken": "spitz",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The bird life had flitted.",
      "signature": ".abdefhilrt",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "There was no defending it.",
      "signature": ".adefghinorstw",
      "openingToken": "there",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Thornton rose to his feet.",
      "signature": ".efhinorst",
      "openingToken": "thornton",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Upon that he was resolved.",
      "signature": ".adehlnoprstuvw",
      "openingToken": "upon",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"It seems scarcely a house.",
      "signature": ".\"acehilmorstuy",
      "openingToken": "it",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"The twinkling of the what?",
      "signature": "?\"aefghiklnotw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "And he did it deliberately.",
      "signature": ".abdehilnrty",
      "openingToken": "and",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Billee was crying as usual.",
      "signature": ".abcegilnrsuwy",
      "openingToken": "billee",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "From that time forward, Mr.",
      "signature": ",.adefhimortw",
      "openingToken": "from",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "His tongue had tricked him.",
      "signature": ".acdeghikmnorstu",
      "openingToken": "his",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "It seemed a mite top-heavy.",
      "signature": "-.adehimopstvy",
      "openingToken": "it",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Shall I try the experiment?",
      "signature": "?aehilmnprstxy",
      "openingToken": "shall",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "That club was a revelation.",
      "signature": ".abcehilnorstuvw",
      "openingToken": "that",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The runners are froze fast.",
      "signature": ".aefhnorstuz",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "There was no opposing them.",
      "signature": ".aeghimnoprstw",
      "openingToken": "there",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "You know the song, perhaps?",
      "signature": ",?aeghknoprstuwy",
      "openingToken": "you",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\" was heard in the distance.",
      "signature": ".\"acdehinrstw",
      "openingToken": "was",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "It seemed natural and human.",
      "signature": ".adehilmnrstu",
      "openingToken": "it",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Mebbe all mad dog, sacredam!",
      "signature": ",!abcdeglmors",
      "openingToken": "mebbe",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The man came back hurriedly.",
      "signature": ".abcdehiklmnrtuy",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Things no longer went right.",
      "signature": ".eghilnorstw",
      "openingToken": "things",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"There was a third enclosure?",
      "signature": "?\"acdehilnorstuw",
      "openingToken": "there",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "It seemed like a conjuration.",
      "signature": ".acdeijklmnorstu",
      "openingToken": "it",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Manuel had one besetting sin.",
      "signature": ".abdeghilmnostu",
      "openingToken": "manuel",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Small indeed was my appetite.",
      "signature": ".adeilmnpstwy",
      "openingToken": "small",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "The squirrels were in hiding.",
      "signature": ".deghilnqrstuw",
      "openingToken": "the",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Is there never anything else?",
      "signature": "?\"aeghilnrstvy",
      "openingToken": "is",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Only an invitation to dinner.",
      "signature": ".\"adeilnortvy",
      "openingToken": "only",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spitz was a practised fighter.",
      "signature": ".acdefghiprstwz",
      "openingToken": "spitz",
      "tokenCount": 5,
      "difficultyBand": "developing"
    }
  ]
}